<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.4">
<l>aṅkō rāykkulat tuḷva ḷarntuceṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṅkōr tāyuru vāki vantavaḷ</l>
<l>koṅkai naṉcuṇṭa kōyiṉ maikolō</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷ veṅkatir cīṟu kiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having arrived and been raised there among a cowherd clan,</l>
<l>Was it an injustice when [he] ate the poison of the breast</l>
<l>Of a woman who came there, taking a mother’s form?</l>
<l>The moon’s hot rays are blazing!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
